     (2) r<m bound: from each 2x'<=m, 4*(a'^2+..+d'^2) <= 4m^2 => sum <= m^2 => r<=m.
     (3) Euler identity on (m*p)*(m*r)=w^2+x^2+y^2+z^2 (proveStarFor on witnesses),
